  <aside><p>Choosing a trainer is important to giving you and your dog the best chance for success with your training goals. Considering location, hours, pricing and training philosophy will help you find a trainer that works for you. After all, training your dog is about making your life easier and developing a better relationship with your dog. </p>
  <em>Explore the trainers in the area.</em></aside></div>
